            "reviewGeneral": {
              "raw": "{\"data\":{},\"content\":[{\"data\":{},\"content\":[{\"data\":{},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"bold\"}],\"value\":\"Summary\",\"nodeType\":\"text\"}],\"nodeType\":\"heading-5\"},{\"data\":{},\"content\":[{\"data\":{},\"marks\":[],\"value\":\"Avenger Mordred is a long range backline DPS, specialised at killing strikers and Corrupted Objects (COs). She has unique targeting priority against strikers, bind and some damage-reducing debuffs, but no survivability mechanics beyond slightly above average stats.\",\"nodeType\":\"text\"}],\"nodeType\":\"paragraph\"},{\"data\":{},\"content\":[{\"data\":{},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"bold\"}],\"value\":\"PVE Review\",\"nodeType\":\"text\"}],\"nodeType\":\"heading-5\"},{\"data\":{},\"content\":[{\"data\":{},\"marks\":[],\"value\":\"Mordred excels against enemies typed as COs. Her dps against these enemies is close to Eve Meitner. She also has an extremely high damage special that lends well to the burst oriented strategies Danger Close is known for. Overall Mordred is an explosive damage dealer against COs but middling against everything else.\",\"nodeType\":\"text\"}],\"nodeType\":\"paragraph\"},{\"data\":{},\"content\":[{\"data\":{},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"bold\"}],\"value\":\"PVP Review\",\"nodeType\":\"text\"}],\"nodeType\":\"heading-5\"},{\"data\":{},\"content\":[{\"data\":{},\"marks\":[],\"value\":\"In PVP Mordred is the nuclear solution to striker metagame. Incidentally, she also happens to be good against CO frontline units, but those don't see much play.  Properly geared, her special is capable of one-shotting all enemies without MDL and targeting priority against strikers means there isn't much counterplay involved. However her performance against everything else is subpar, making her a tech option.\",\"nodeType\":\"text\"}],\"nodeType\":\"paragraph\"}],\"nodeType\":\"document\"}"
            },
